query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(t tq q) NoMergeJoin(q t tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.name IN ('applescript',
'babeljs',
'css-float',
'cypher',
'entity-framework-5',
'generator',
'grid',
'ios10',
'jquery-selectors',
'liferay',
'llvm',
'pdf-generation',
'request',
'textarea',
'wsdl')
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow');
